# HADF Phase 2-bis Sub-exp 1 — cloud-AI API keys
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. Copy this file to .env.local (in the SAME directory):
#        cp .env.local.template .env.local
#   2. Mint a fresh API key from each provider's console (links below)
#   3. Replace each "<paste...>" placeholder with the real key
#   4. SAVE the file
#   5. Tell Claude "ready" — Claude will:
#        - compute sha256 of .env.local
#        - patch the pre-reg
#        - run lock-prereg.sh + smoke-fire
#
# NOTES:
#   - This file is .gitignored (.env.local is never committed)
#   - Phase 2 pattern was shell-export; Phase 2-bis Fix #2 mandates .env.local
#     as a regular file (NOT symlink) in the worktree
#   - Keep this file local — never paste it into chat, PR, or any other surface

# ── REQUIRED for Sub-exp 1 (9 endpoints, 6 providers) ──

# OpenAI — 2 endpoints: gpt-4o-mini, gpt-4o
# Mint at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Format: sk-proj-...  (starts with sk-proj or sk-)
OPENAI_API_KEY=<paste OpenAI key here>

# Anthropic — 2 endpoints: claude-haiku-4-5, claude-sonnet-4-6
# Mint at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Format: sk-ant-api03-...
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=<paste Anthropic key here>

# Google — 2 endpoints: gemini-2-flash, gemini-2-pro
# Mint at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Format: AIza...
# (Either GOOGLE_API_KEY or GEMINI_API_KEY works; the script falls back automatically)
GOOGLE_API_KEY=<paste Google AI Studio key here>

# Mistral — 1 endpoint: mistral-large-latest
# Mint at: https://console.mistral.ai/api-keys
# Format: alphanumeric ~32 chars
MISTRAL_API_KEY=<paste Mistral key here>

# xAI — 1 endpoint: grok-4-1
# Mint at: https://console.x.ai
# Format: xai-...
XAI_API_KEY=<paste xAI key here>

# Vercel AI Gateway — 1 endpoint: gpt-4o-mini via gateway
# Mint at: https://vercel.com/dashboard/ai-gateway (your team or personal scope)
# Format: vai-...  (or check Vercel dashboard for current format)
VERCEL_AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=<paste Vercel AI Gateway key here>

# Optional: override default Vercel AI Gateway base URL (rarely needed)
# VERCEL_AI_GATEWAY_BASE_URL=https://ai-gateway.vercel.sh/v1
